Uses of Package
for_final_project

  • Classes in for_final_project used by for_final_project 
    Class and Description
    BirthDate
    A BirthDate object defines a birthday as a month, day, and year, where month, day, and year are each of the type int.
    BirthInfo
    A BirthInfo object defines complete birthday information as a name plus a birthday, where the name is a Name object and birthday is a BirthDate object.
    BirthInfo.ChronComp
    An inner class for a ChronComp object that orders BirthInfos by the alternative, chronological ordering scheme of BirthDates using the Comparator interface
    BirthInfoCollection
    A BirthInfoCollection object defines a collection of BirthInfos as an alphabetically ordered binary tree of BirthInfos and a chronologically ordered binary tree of BirthInfos.
    Name
    A Name object defines a name as a first, middle, and family name, where first, middle and family names are all of type string.
